trans-unit.source: Represents the AppSequence header defined in the WS-Discovery protocol.
trans-unit.target: 表示 WS-Discovery 通訊協定中定義的 AppSequence 標頭。

trans-unit.source: This class allows a receiver of discovery messages to process those messages in order even though they were received out of order.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別允許探索訊息接收者依順序處理這些訊息，即使訊息並未依照順序接收。

trans-unit.source: The discovery message sequence to compare.
trans-unit.target: 要比較的探索訊息序列。

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the specified <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> instance is comparable to the current <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 取得值，這個值表示指定的 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> 執行個體是否可與目前的 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> 執行個體比較。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the two discovery message sequences are comparable; otherwise <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果兩個探索訊息序列可以比較，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The discovery message sequence to compare.
trans-unit.target: 要比較的探索訊息序列。

trans-unit.source: Compares the specified <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> instance with the current <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 比較指定的 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> 執行個體與目前的 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> 執行個體。

trans-unit.source: 0 if the two discovery message sequences are equal, a negative number if the message number of <paramref name="other" /> is greater than the message number of the current discovery sequence.
trans-unit.target: 如果兩個探索訊息序列相等，則為 0；如果 <paramref name="other" /> 的訊息號碼大於目前探索序列的訊息號碼，則為負數。

trans-unit.source: Determines if the specified object is equal to the current <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 判斷指定的物件是否等於目前的 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> 執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The object to compare.
trans-unit.target: 要比較的物件。

trans-unit.source: Determines if the specified object is equal to the current <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 判斷指定的物件是否等於目前的 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> 執行個體。

trans-unit.source: true if the specified object is equal to the current discovery message sequence.
trans-unit.target: 如果指定的物件等於目前的探索訊息序列，則為 true。

trans-unit.source: The discovery message sequence to compare.
trans-unit.target: 要比較的探索訊息序列。

trans-unit.source: Determines if the specified <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> instance is comparable to the current <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 判斷指定的 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> 執行個體是否可與目前的 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> 執行個體比較。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the two discovery message sequences are comparable; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果兩個探索訊息序列可以比較，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets a hash code for the current <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 取得目前 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> 執行個體的雜湊碼。

trans-unit.source: A hash code value.
trans-unit.target: 雜湊碼值。

trans-unit.source: Gets the instance ID.
trans-unit.target: 取得執行個體 ID。

trans-unit.source: The instance ID.
trans-unit.target: 執行個體 ID。

trans-unit.source: This value is incremented each time the service is shut down or loses state.
trans-unit.target: 這個值會在每次服務關閉或失去狀態時遞增。

trans-unit.source: Gets the message number.
trans-unit.target: 取得訊息號碼。

trans-unit.source: The message number.
trans-unit.target: 訊息號碼。

trans-unit.source: This value identifies a message within the context of a sequence identifier and an instance identifier.
trans-unit.target: 這個值會在序列識別碼和執行個體識別碼的內容內識別訊息。

trans-unit.source: A discovery message sequence.
trans-unit.target: 探索訊息序列。

trans-unit.source: A discovery message sequence.
trans-unit.target: 探索訊息序列。

trans-unit.source: Determines if two specified instances of <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> are equal.
trans-unit.target: 判斷兩個指定的 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> 執行個體是否相等。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the two discovery message sequence instances are equal; otherwise <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果兩個探索訊息序列的執行個體相等，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.target: 探索訊息序列。

trans-unit.source: Determines if two specified instances of <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> are not equal.
trans-unit.target: 判斷兩個指定的 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence" /> 執行個體是否不相等。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the two discovery message sequence instances are not equal; otherwise <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果兩個探索訊息序列的執行個體不相等，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets the sequence ID.
trans-unit.target: 取得序列 ID。

trans-unit.target: 序列 ID。

trans-unit.source: This value identifies a sequence within the context of an instance identifier.
trans-unit.target: 此值會在執行個體識別碼的內容內識別序列。
